Package org.proto4j.graph

Class BracketConstraints

java.lang.Object
org.proto4j.graph.BracketConstraints
All Implemented Interfaces:
BracketLocator
public final class BracketConstraints
extends java.lang.Object
implements BracketLocator
The BracketConstraints class specifies constraints either for the BracketLocator or BracketLinePainter to use when painting the parent JBracketView.
See Also:
BracketLocator, JBracketView
